### 2. Check Identity Verification Status
### Returns the current identity verification status for authenticated user
### Requires: Authentication (JWT token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/verification/identity/status
Authorization: {{token}}

### Expected Response (Verified):
# {
#   "success": true,
#   "isVerified": true,
#   "details": {
#     "idType": "driving_license",
#     "verifiedName": "John Smith",
#     "verifiedDOB": "1990-05-15",
#     "licenseNumber": "SMITH905156JD9XX",
#     "verifiedAt": "2025-12-06T14:30:00.000Z"
