### 4. Stripe Webhook Endpoint
### This endpoint receives webhook events from Stripe Identity
### DO NOT call this manually - only Stripe should call this
### See README.md for webhook setup instructions
POST {{baseUrl}}/verification/identity/webhook
stripe-signature: whsec_test_signature_from_stripe
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "evt_test_webhook",
  "type": "identity.verification_session.verified",
  "data": {
    "object": {
      "id": "vs_1QNqYX2eZvKYlo2C8H7zg123",
      "status": "verified"
    }
  }
}

### Expected Response:
# {
#   "received": true
# }

### Note: This endpoint validates the Stripe signature
### Invalid signatures will return 500 error


